### Low Severity Findings

#### 9. General Fixture (Over-broad Setup)
**Class-level** (line 11, 19)

```csharp
private FakeLogger _logger = null!;
// initialized in Setup, never used by any test method
```

**Problem:** Every test pays the cost of constructing `_logger` even though none need it. Signals an incomplete or abandoned test plan.

**Fix:** Remove `_logger` from the shared fixture. Add it only to tests that need it.

