### Prioritized Remediation Plan

| Priority | Smell | Effort | Rationale |
|----------|-------|--------|-----------|
| 1 | Assertion-Free Test | Low | Immediate risk — false-passing test |
| 2 | Mystery Guest | Low | Blocks CI — test cannot pass outside one machine |
| 3 | Conditional Test Logic | Medium | Hidden coverage gap |
| 4 | Sleepy Test | Medium | Flakiness source + 2s suite slowdown |
| 5 | Exception Handling | Low | Quick swap to `ThrowsException<T>` |
| 6 | General Fixture | Low | Delete one unused field |
| 7 | Magic Number + Assertion Roulette | Medium | Readability & diagnostics |
| 8 | Sensitive Equality | Medium | Fragile to format changes |
| 9 | Eager Test | High | Requires decomposition into focused tests |

